# Master AI Instructions

This directory contains the single source of truth for AI tool instructions.

## Files

- `system-info.md.tmpl` - System context (OS, shell, environment)
- `code-style.md.tmpl` - Code style preferences and conventions
- `plan-discipline.md.tmpl` - Plan file hygiene rules (date-prefixed, never-overwrite, archive)

## Usage

Include these files in tool-specific configs:

```
{{- $systemInfo := include "dot_config/ai-context/system-info.md.tmpl" }}
{{- $codeStyle := include "dot_config/ai-context/code-style.md.tmpl" }}
{{- $planDiscipline := include "dot_config/ai-context/plan-discipline.md.tmpl" }}
{{ $systemInfo }}
{{ $codeStyle }}
{{ $planDiscipline }}
```

## Tools Using These Configs

- Claude Code: `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md` (via `private_dot_claude/CLAUDE.md.tmpl`)
- Gemini CLI: `~/.gemini/GEMINI.md` (via `dot_local/share/private_gemini/GEMINI.md.tmpl`)
- Global AGENTS.md: `~/AGENTS.md` (via `AGENTS.md.tmpl` at chezmoi root)
- GitHub Copilot: `~/.config/ai-instructions/copilot-instructions.md`
- Cursor: `~/.config/ai-instructions/cursor-rules/core.mdc`
